# Build-context excludes for `gcloud run deploy --source .`.
# The Dockerfile only COPYs: pyproject.toml, README.md, advocate/, agent_apps/,
# and the four demo CSVs (climate + fintech) — everything else is upload bloat
# for Cloud Build.
#
# NOTE: once this file exists, gcloud no longer auto-reads .gitignore, so we
# pull it in explicitly and add the heavy dirs it doesn't cover.
#!include:.gitignore

.git/
.claude/
.firecrawl/
docs/
tasks/
tests/
.coverage
